It's fairly limited currently as it can only move in one direction and the rails lasts only for 100-200 blocks.

Map.name: Sonic the Hedgehog: The Chaos Quest

Sonic is the fastest, Tails jumps highest, and Knuckles is the strongest! Please note that pictures shown lack the resource pack, since I was unable to make it work.
